title: 4 Year Anniversary Live Show in NYC
itunes:author: Loud Speakers Network
itunes:summary:
On this week's episode of #TheFriendZone, we share the live audio from our 4 Year Anniversary Live Show at the New School Auditorium in NYC. Hosted by Mouse Jones and DJ GabSoul. And featuring our brilliant and hilarious friends JadeofAllJades + Xavier D'Leau of Jade + XD, Mandii of Whoreible Decisions and Kidfury + Crissle of The Read. Thank you to everyone who attended! 

Thank you to our Sponsors:

Ben & Jerry's - Treat yourself to your favorite flavor anywhere ice cream is sold or find a new favorite at https://www.benjerry.com

A Black Lady Sketch Show - HBO's newest comedy is A Black Lady Sketch Show - written by, directed by, and starring black ladies. A groundbreaking new comedy series starring a core black female cast and celebrity guests portraying dozens of dynamic characters and hyper-versions of themselves in a magical reality. Airs Friday nights at 11 pm, only on HBO.

Talkspace - We all need someone to talk to - a person who can support us through rough patches or even the everyday ups and downs of life. That's where Talkspace comes in. Therapy for how we live today - mobile, affordable, and available when you need it. Use code ZONE to get $65 off your first month and show support for the show.

Follow us online:

Twitter - https://twitter.com/FriendZonePod
Facebook - https://www.facebook.com/TheFriendZonePodcast

Have a GREAT day!
